# codeplug-tool edits

Read [`AGENTS.md`](../../AGENTS.md) first. For git, plans, and docs see [`.cursor/skills/`](../skills/).

## Vendor boundaries

Internal model, store, mutations, validation, and CRUD UI are **vendor-neutral** — no radio profile constants or member-count caps. Cardinality limits, truncation, and column mapping belong at **`src/lib/import/`** and **`src/lib/export/`** only. See [AGENTS.md — Vendor boundaries](../../AGENTS.md#vendor-boundaries).

## SPA (`src/`)

- React + TypeScript under `src/`; Vite bundles for GitHub Pages (`base: '/codeplug-tool/'`).
- Routing via `react-router` HashRouter.
- Build info via Vite `define` — see [version-number skill](../skills/version-number/SKILL.md).

## Channel map

- UI: `src/components/ChannelMap/ChannelMap.tsx`
- Parsing and geometry: `src/lib/csv.ts`, `src/lib/channels.ts`, `src/lib/geo.ts`
- Route: `/#/map` via `src/routes/Map.tsx`
- Parse OpenGD77 CSV by **column header name**, not index.
- Zone hulls use the same coordinate filters as channel markers (`Use Location`, skip `0,0`).
- A channel may appear in multiple zones — each zone hull includes shared members independently.
- Mapbox tokens: `localStorage` only; never commit tokens or require a server.

## Scope

- GitHub Pages deploy is release-triggered — see `docs/build/README.md`.
- Do not add committed sample codeplugs; use gitignored `sample-exports/` for local CSVs.
